    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anthèse</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a broken world. Become the hope of those who survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anthèse is an Action Light RPG adventure game, the fruit of a 4-month graduation project by a team of 11 passionate French students.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where humanity has taken refuge on floating islands after a catastrophe called the Fracture, you play as 21-year-old Emöke, a Flesh-forged Guardian with a troubled past, always accompanied by her faithful mount. Charged with protecting the last human strongholds, she is sent on a mission to an island threatened by a fearsome predator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077480/extras/7081e9d3711a5a60170bc1c8fb9e2715.avif?t=1750873589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077480/extras_big/7081e9d3711a5a60170bc1c8fb9e2715.avif?t=1750873589 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face savage enemies in a gameplay blending Mob Bashing and intense Boss Fights, explore a ruined universe marked by the scars of the past, and plunge into the heart of a conflict of ideologies that will shake your convictions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077480/extras/a76de27bcb265f91de90f31e3f6bcbc3.avif?t=1750873589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077480/extras_big/a76de27bcb265f91de90f31e3f6bcbc3.avif?t=1750873589 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of Emöke in third-person view, whether you play with the Xbox controller, PlayStation or keyboard. In combat, alternate between precise dodging, hand-to-hand sword attacks and a ranged attack triggered by your mount. Use healing kits to recover life. Every battle demands responsiveness, resource management and a sense of timing to survive in a merciless world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077480/extras/7e42d348797fbdbde53df882e0d8d761.avif?t=1750873589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077480/extras_big/7e42d348797fbdbde53df882e0d8d761.avif?t=1750873589 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
